    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "that sounds nice but it feels like a lie. doctors always say there's hope, but i feel like my neurobiology is just a constant loop of suffering. if my brain chemistry is literally programmed to be this way, isn't \"cultivating a state of mind\" just fighting a losing battle against physics? like, if the hardware is flawed, how can the software ever actually work?",
